title: Spanish Style House Share - West Hollywood
posting_body: ['Very spacious 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath Spanish style home - Available September/October 2022', 'This is a shared home, no couples, no pets, no smoking.', '  The home is professionally designed and fully furnished.', 'Seeking a professional housemate.', 'Located in the heart of West Hollywood.', ' (Two blocks north of Melrose and three blocks South of Santa Monica Blvd.)', ' This is an ideal location for anyone who enjoys walking to coffee shops, restaurants, great shopping and sight seeing.', 'Areas Include:', 'Living Room', 'Dining Room', 'TV Lounge', 'Laundry Room', 'Picnic Area', 'Garage/Art Studio/Gym', 'Amenities include:  washer/dryer, air conditioning, heat.', 'Serious inquiries only.', '  Must include social media handle or send resume and photo when connecting.', "Additional fee's are:  Parking passes and Wifi.", 'Thank you,', 'Matt']
